_sText:
This is a slightly better version of a map I created years and years ago. So please expect some bad frame rates and other issues in general. The old version was not even compiled on full and did not contain many func_detail brushes at all. This version however, is compiled on full and i have converted a few complex brushes to props to help with the fps.

Since this map was created i have learn't alot and the only reason for it being updated is because of some pestering messages i have received via youtube.
